component_text: saving some part of your earnings is essential
you can not predict future developments, neither in your professional nor your personal life, furthermore with savings you can fulfill some of your dreams
there are several uncertainties about your professional future
The global economic conditions in these days are tough and there are many unpredictable factors that make it necessary to have some money on your bank account
I remember some friends who lost their jobs recently due to the economic crisis in Europe
They could not afford the rent
they had to move back in with their families and they lost their independence
you can not be sure about the development in your personal life
It is possible that in the future you have some unavoidable expenses that you could not afford without savings
Back in university I remember a friend of mine who had just little savings and he had to deal with a major repair of his car
He could not afford the maintenance
with savings you can afford some luxurious goods and fulfill your dreams
Working hard and saving money for later on investments is a great way of getting a satisfying feeling and to reward yourself for something you have accomplished
I made a month-long backpack trip through Southeast Asia last summer with my girlfriend
Without our savings we could not have pursued our long-time dream
there is no other choice than saving money for some time
